<concept id="r_psdk_ad-signaling-mode"> 
  <title>Ad signaling mode</title> 
  <shortdesc>The ad signaling mode specifies where the video stream should get
	 advertising information. 
  </shortdesc> 
  <conbody> 
	 <p>The valid values are <codeph>PTAdSignalingModeDefault</codeph>,
				<codeph>PTAdSignalingModeManifestCues</codeph>, and
				<codeph>PTAdSignalingModeServerMap</codeph>. </p> 
